{"tid":1781702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母有手足被狗告係屋企收埋兩把刀仲屈埋入小欖，最後撤控","createTime":"2019-12-13T10:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T15:51:49.000Z","uid":125168,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7f78fbba0b3fe69333f6aed2726a250a6c3e47c7","tid":1781702,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"電腦技術員今年10月在facebook賬戶分享美國槍擊案新聞，並揚言會效法。警方接報，及後上門到其西環住所調查，在屋內檢獲兩把刀，其中一把刀身刻有「MY ELF WEAPON」。技術員被控管有攻擊性武器罪，更一度還押小欖精神病治療中心候查。惟案件今在東區裁判法院再提訊時，控方指經過調查及取得法律意見後，認為沒有證據顯示被告有意圖使用涉案刀具在公眾地方作非法用途，故申請撤銷起訴，並將涉案刀具歸還被告。裁判官照准，被告當庭釋放。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191213/60372966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191213%2F60372966&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6lm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=2d1e0114\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191213%2F60372966&h=d16d9534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191213/60372966</a>"},{"pid":"a16e3404a74e3100355edc8d9d4ae18eca8d2961","tid":1781702,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:00:32.000Z","msg":"另外一單：<br />\n<br />\n反修例衝突持續半年，警方拘捕超過6千人，當中近8成都未檢控，包括8月在銅鑼灣，喬裝警員拘捕的一批「極端核心暴力示威者」，當中大部分人已經踢保。"},{"pid":"b8e6f96f5d0b2ac90a52c95973c3391c50b1cf53","tid":1781702,"uid":167928,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"未必一定係手足"},{"pid":"b68a9a3f5619595ee50365b3690fdc8a571d3c06","tid":1781702,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b8e6f96f5d0b2ac90a52c95973c3391c50b1cf53","tid":1781702,"uid":167928,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"未必一定係手足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"你啱，但狗濫捕呢個人都係想嚇手足"},{"pid":"2a1509791ea54cf3c0c66d3f8284a450c5926453","tid":1781702,"uid":39277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:03:32.000Z","msg":"遲啲好似元朝咁<br />\n十戶人用一把刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2749b0d3231da3694c5d4cf281a8fb46d0fb6206","tid":1781702,"uid":330626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:04:08.000Z","msg":"黑警濫捕都已經係家常便飯<br />\n成撚日拉完又告唔入 on99"},{"pid":"02f39891a7f8e18d6b93d3c2759b47e5338f526a","tid":1781702,"uid":37869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"法治有險可守<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/society/廚房藏菜刀被捕-投訴警一年無下文-中年婦斥警-邊個刀唔係放廚房/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF%E8%97%8F%E8%8F%9C%E5%88%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E5%A9%A6%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6-%E9%82%8A%E5%80%8B%E5%88%80%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E6%94%BE%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF%2F&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6lm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=8393ff40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF%E8%97%8F%E8%8F%9C%E5%88%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E5%A9%A6%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6-%E9%82%8A%E5%80%8B%E5%88%80%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E6%94%BE%E5%BB%9A%E6%88%BF%2F&h=d0d00015\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandnews.com/society/廚房藏菜刀被捕-投訴警一年無下文-中年婦斥警-邊個刀唔係放廚房/</a><br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n屯門山景邨一名婦人去年與房署管理公司發生爭執，及後警方竟以「廚房有菜刀」為證據，指控她刑事恐嚇。婦人又指在拘留期間，警員拒絕讓她飲水及如廁，令她只能在地上小便。她事後向投訴警察課作投訴，但將近一年後至今仍無下文。<br />\n.............................<br />\n<br />\n翌日案件提堂，主控官更以她有精神病為由，申請把她還押至小欖精神病治療中心，以等候精神評估報告。馮女士因而在中心渡過16日，最終報告指她無精神問題。至今年1月裁判官認為證人口供矛盾，判馮女士無須答辯當庭釋放，更批評主控官在證據薄弱下提控是浪費公帑。"},{"pid":"39c0bfad1e18ae1c94dffa88484e394755017f3f","tid":1781702,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2749b0d3231da3694c5d4cf2